OL,3,CDuty of candour in NHS 'needs urgent
OL,4,Creview', inquiry told
OL,6,FDuty of candour in the NHS is not
OL,7,Fworking and needs replacing with
OL,8,Fstronger powers, a former senior
OL,9,Fombudsman has told the inquiry over
OL,10,Fthe crimes of child serial killer
OL,11,Fnurse Lucy Letby.
OL,13,FSir Rob Behrens said that fines for
OL,14,Fhealth and social care providers were
OL,15,F"so puny" they were not acting as a
OL,16,Fdeterrent against complying with the
OL,17,Fstatutory obligation to be open and
OL,18,Ftransparent with patients and their
OL,19,Ffamilies.
