OL,3,CDuty of candour in NHS 'needs urgent
OL,4,Creview', inquiry told
OL,6,FGiving evidence to the Thirlwall
OL,7,FInquiry, the Parliamentary and Health
OL,8,FService Ombudsman between April 2017
OL,9,Fand March 2024 said: "The duty of
OL,10,Fcandour does not work and needs urgent
OL,11,Freviewing and replacement with
OL,12,Fstronger powers.
OL,14,F"It doesn't work because it doesn't
OL,15,Fapply to individuals. It applies to
OL,16,Fpersons and that is interpreted as a
OL,17,Fpublic body.
