OL,4,Creview', inquiry told
OL,6,F"Secondly, the fines issued are so
OL,7,Fpuny that it doesn't have impact on
OL,8,Fthe behaviour of the leaders of the
OL,9,F(NHS) trust."
OL,11,FHe added: "Time and time again, we
OL,12,Fhave seen senior managers and boards
OL,13,Fare more interested in preserving the
OL,14,Freputation of their organisation
OL,15,Frather than dealing with patient
OL,16,Fsafety issues.
