OL,6,FSir Rob said current whistleblowing
OL,7,Flaws in England were also not working,
OL,8,Fwith doctors fearing the end of their
OL,9,Fcareers if they spoke out.
OL,11,FHe told the inquiry: "Too often in my
OL,12,Fexperience, doctors who want to
OL,13,Fdisclose patient safety issues are
OL,14,Fdisciplined or threatened with
OL,15,Fdiscipline by the leadership of the
OL,16,Ftrust and the board, and this means
OL,17,Fthey are extremely vulnerable when
OL,18,Fthey do blow the whistle.
OL,26,@sD@VOU
