OL,3,CDuty of candour in NHS 'needs urgent
OL,4,Creview', inquiry told
OL,6,F"Unlike in Scotland, there is no
OL,7,Fopportunity for people who want to
OL,8,Fblow the whistle to have a body that
OL,9,Fthey can go to in order to get support
OL,10,Fand advice.
OL,12,F"The whistleblowers I have met feel
OL,13,Fisolated and vulnerable when they do
OL,14,Fblow the whistle because of bad
OL,15,Fexperiences that so many of them have
OL,16,Fhad.
