OL,4,Creview', inquiry told
OL,6,F"If you look at the litigation costs
OL,7,Fand the compensation fees around
OL,8,Fwhistleblowing issues, they are
OL,9,Fenormous. It's not productive to
OL,10,Fhandle cases in this aggressive way."
OL,12,FHe said Freedom to Speak Up Guardians
OL,13,Fin the NHS did a "brilliant job" but
OL,14,Fsome had told him they themselves did
OL,15,Fnot feel able to be frank and open
OL,16,Fabout their own experiences for fear
OL,17,Fthey too would be disciplined.
