OL,7,Ftrust leaders have said to me 'you are
OL,8,Fundermining us by pointing out that
OL,9,Fwhat we are doing is wrong and people
OL,10,Fwon't trust us if you keep on doing
OL,11,Fthis'.
OL,13,F"You have to acknowledge where things
