OL,6,F"One of the great things that I have
OL,7,Flearnt as ombudsman is the heroic
OL,8,Fbehaviour of parents and family
OL,9,Fmembers in seeking to keep cases going
OL,10,Fwhich otherwise would have fallen by
OL,11,Fthe wayside, and that should not be
OL,12,Fthe case.
OL,14,F"Parents in this case are to be hugely
OL,15,Fcommended for their courage and
OL,16,Ftenacity in taking this forward. It is
OL,17,Ffrightening to think how many cases
OL,18,Fwould have just disappeared without
OL,19,Ftheir continuity."
