OL,6,FNo complaints regarding patient care
OL,7,Fat the Countess of Chester's neonatal
OL,8,Funit were made to the ombudsman in
OL,9,F2015 and 2016 when Letby attacked
OL,10,Finfants in her care, the inquiry heard.
OL,12,FConsultant paediatricians voiced fears
OL,13,Fto hospital bosses that the nurse was
OL,14,Fdeliberately harming babies following
OL,15,Fthe deaths of two triplet boys in June
OL,16,F2016 but police were not called in
OL,17,Funtil May 2017.
